embeddedItem.name: Conqueror's Will
embeddedItem.desc: Condensed anti-matter. Advanced material used for enhancement.
embeddedItem.lore:
Highly condensed anti-matter within the body of the Voidranger: Trampler. The moment of obliteration is the trumpet call for civilizations' destruction.

"They are all looking forward to the moment of obliteration, when they will be reforged and fused with the entire world."
comeFrom: Antimatter Legion at Equilibrium Level 4 or higher

29328.name: Credit
29328.desc: This currency, used by the Interastral Peace Corporation to settle accounts with its customers, is now widely accepted as the hard currency for space travel.
29328.lore: "People run around fighting and trading for numbers in a terminal, but the truly precious cannot be bought."

39352.name: Carve the Moon, Weave the Clouds
39352.desc: Light Cone for the Path of Harmony. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
39352.lore:
He immediately falls in love with the golden vessel and is about to buy it,
but the Foxian girl drags him aside and whispers:
"Please return at night, Mr. Benefactor, and make up your mind then."

As promised, he returns at night.
The same Foxian girl opens the door and smiles at him.
"Please follow me, Mr. Benefactor."

A ray of moonlight shines onto the base of the etched plate.
The artisan had traced the petals with lines of various depths, and he would not be able to see such details without the moonlight.

He finally recalls why this item is called "Carve the Moon, Weave the Clouds."

39354.name: This Is Me!
39354.desc: Light Cone for the Path of Preservation. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
39354.lore:
The girl could rock any outfit she chooses, but she was unsatisfied, judging by the dozen sets of clothing piled up behind her.

"Will this be the last outfit for today?"

She thought silently to herself and looked at the girl in the mirror. She looked extra happy on this day.

"Okay! This is me!"

79823.name: Patience Is All You Need
79823.desc: Light Cone for the Path of Nihility. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
79823.lore:
"Could it be that there's something you haven't told me?"

She watches as their neck stiffens, as if a lump is blocking their throat.
She knows she is feared, and that no further step is needed.
At this point, it no longer mattered what she said.
Any word she utters radiates horror...
They stand no chance against her, and have no choice but to blurt out what she wants to hear.

Like a spider waiting in its web, patience is all she needs.

79828.name: In the Night
79828.desc: Light Cone for the Path of The Hunt. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
79828.lore:
A young girl smiles subtly.
"How?"
"Right here, right now, I am alone..."
"But it feels... very lively."

175480.name: March 7th
175480.lore:
A girl who once slumbered in eternal ice and knows nothing about her past.
To find out the truth about her origins, she decided to travel with the Astral Express.
As of right now, she has prepared about 67 different versions of her life story for herself.

175713.name: Trailblazer
175713.lore:
A girl/boy who boarded the Astral Express.
They chose to travel with the Astral Express to eliminate the dangers posed by the Stellaron.

196472.name: Sleep Like the Dead
196472.desc: Light Cone for the Path of The Hunt. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
196472.lore:
The boy is still tightly grasping the sword even when fast asleep against the general's shoulder.
The general gently taps the boy's cheek, and the boy mutters in his sleep.
"General... I finally... won."

The general pauses. He suddenly realizes that, compared to the boy trying to improve every day,
he himself has endured too many years and is used to stagnation.

"You will soon be better than everyone, and that will only be the beginning..."

270122.name: Yanqing
270122.lore:
General Jing Yuan's retainer. A gifted swordsman who hasn't even come of age.
No one can best Yanqing when he holds a sword in hand.

376299.name: Trailblazer
376299.lore:
A girl/boy who boarded the Astral Express.
They chose to travel with the Astral Express to eliminate the dangers posed by the Stellaron.

454626.name: Seele
454626.lore:
A resident of the Underworld and the backbone of Wildfire. She goes by the alias "Babochka."
She has a frank personality, but there is a delicate and sensitive hidden side to her deep in her heart.

460240.name: Trailblazer
460240.lore:
A girl/boy who boarded the Astral Express.
They chose to travel with the Astral Express to eliminate the dangers posed by the Stellaron.

500482.name: Qingque
500482.lore:
Diviner of the Divination Commission on the Xianzhou Luofu, and a librarian.
Always slacks off and is about to be demoted to a "door guardian."

633378.name: Usurper's Scheme
633378.desc: A moderate amount of anti-matter. Normal material used for enhancement.
633378.lore:
A moderate amount of anti-matter that floats around the Voidranger: Distorter. The amount of matter and anti-matter particles has reached a dangerous balance...

"They are all looking forward to the moment of obliteration, when they will be reforged and fused with the entire world."
comeFrom: Antimatter Legion at Equilibrium Level 2 or higher

676267.name: Defense
676267.desc: Light Cone for the Path of Preservation. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
676267.lore:
A drop of strength condensed from time itself. All the seemingly insignificant moments come together to form the magnificent choir of fate.

"If you ever doubt these walls will lead us to victory, just look at these brave souls standing atop them."

717289.name: Silvermane Medal
717289.desc: Medal of honor worn by soldiers of the Silvermane Guards with gallant and meritorious service. Advanced material used for enhancement.
717289.lore:
A proof of honor awarded to those that fought against Fragmentum creatures, Underworlders, and sudden disasters.
It is not usually pinned onto the recipient's chest, but rather placed onto his coffin.

"Remember, young Gepard. It is not a toy: it is the destiny and blood of the Landau family."
comeFrom: Everwinter Shadewalker and Incineration Shadewalker at Equilibrium Level 4 or higher
Silvermane Guards and vagrants at Equilibrium Level 4 or higher

717290.name: Ancient Engine
717290.desc: Mechanical engine left behind from the Old World. Advanced material used for enhancement.
717290.lore:
It uses Geomarrow as the energy source. When powered, it spews wandering auroras, not sparkles.

"Only the Technology Division directly under the Supreme Guardian has access to information regarding the Old World. I lost my privileges after I was fired."
comeFrom: Automatons at Equilibrium Level 4 or higher

717320.name: Squirming Core
717320.desc: The heart of a monster wandering the Fragmentum. Advanced material used for enhancement.
717320.lore:
It is a lesion that breeds evil, the impulse to sin. It is the source of the Fragmentum distortion.
The heart is pulsating slowly, with a residual force powerful enough to cause a new calamity. It's best to destroy it to prevent further troubles.

"It's like a cancer..."
comeFrom: Certain Fragmentum Monsters at Equilibrium Level 4 or higher

717385.name: Artifex's Gyreheart
717385.desc: Components used in Xianzhou's ingenium creations. Advanced material used for enhancement.
717385.lore:
The core of Xianzhou's ingenium technology. The armillary sphere roils and vibrates like the essence of a heart, making the machine think like a living being.

"Do not be startled. Taking away its heart would make him... her?... No, make it lose its sentience and return to its mechanical sources."
comeFrom: Entranced Ingenia at Equilibrium Level 4 or higher

717386.name: Immortal Lumintwig
717386.desc: Deciduous twigs from an ancient divine construct. Advanced material used for enhancement.
717386.lore:
The source of the Xianzhou long-life species' "Endless Lifespan." The remnants of the Aeon of Abundance's influence. After the Three Sufferings, Xianzhou laid in devastation. The Homo celestinae fell as demons, and catastrophes occurred ceaselessly.

"As decreed by the Ten-Lords Commission, all who are near the mara-struck state will be seized by the infernal judges and cast into the Shackling Prison."
comeFrom: Abominations of Abundance at Equilibrium Level 4 or higher

754822.name: The Moles Welcome You
754822.desc: Light Cone for the Path of Destruction. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
754822.lore:
"Moles, moles,"
"Leaving our holes,"
"Smart moles fear naught foes,"
"Moles, moles,"
"Bite your toes!"

792910.name: Collapsing Sky
792910.desc: Light Cone for the Path of Destruction. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
792910.lore:
A drop of strength condensed from time itself. All the seemingly insignificant moments come together to form the magnificent choir of fate.

"The death of all things is as natural as their birth. Time erodes everything, turning all tangible entities to dust."

792912.name: Arrows
792912.desc: Light Cone for the Path of The Hunt. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
792912.lore:
A drop of strength condensed from time itself. All the seemingly insignificant moments come together to form the magnificent choir of fate.

"The hunter's eyes are the clearest when they pull back the bowstring with the arrow nocked."

807012.name: Kafka
807012.lore:
A member of the Stellaron Hunters. A dashing, collected, and professional beauty.
Used the enchantment of Spirit Whisper to set up Trailblazer to absorb the Stellaron.
Her hobby is shopping for and organizing her collection of coats.

838767.name: Planetary Rendezvous
838767.desc: Light Cone for the Path of Harmony. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
838767.lore:
She had no idea what to expect when she first started out on this journey.
All she knew was that she could at long last be rid of the judgmental eyes and petty bickering of her family.
She felt she finally understood what the poet was trying to say.
"One day, we would grow wings and forget what it was like to walk."

The light in her eyes became the glittering stars.

891186.name: Trailblazer
891186.lore:
A girl/boy who boarded the Astral Express.
They chose to travel with the Astral Express to eliminate the dangers posed by the Stellaron.

993498.name: Sagacity
993498.desc: Light Cone for the Path of Erudition. The Light Cone ability is only effective for characters of this Path.
993498.lore:
A drop of strength condensed from time itself. All the seemingly insignificant moments come together to form the magnificent choir of fate.

"Should Wise Ones be unable to abandon their identity as humans, they shall be abandoned by wisdom."
